description:
"Get into the spirit this season with festive – though not entirely real – Christmas comedies that show how Google Search can help save your holiday.

Pop star Jett Jingle’s viral meltdown has landed him in hot water. To save his reputation, he’ll have to do a little community service and save a small town’s annual holiday show. But it’ll take more than a Christmas miracle to charm the town’s frosty mayor and transform one local everyman into a bonafide star. Thankfully with Google Search, new looks are easy to Try On. 
 Starring: Johnny Weir, Phaedra Parks, Bob the Drag Queen and John Lutz
